Yeah! My Usopp Rubber Band did 90%of
the work of taking Giant Jack down!

92
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:55,650
Whoa! Incredible!

93
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:55,650
Whoa!

94
00:07:55,650 --> 00:07:58,070
I'm the only one in the world that has them.

95
00:07:58,070 --> 00:08:00,260
Whoa! Amazing!

96
00:07:58,070 --> 00:07:59,390
Whoa!

97
00:08:02,590 --> 00:08:06,990
